overview:
Accordions are wrappers for <je-link href="../je-details">JeDetails</je-link>. When an inner detail is opened, the others are automatically closed.
The implementation follows the [aria implementation of an accordion](https://www.w3.org/WAI/ARIA/apg/patterns/accordion/).
docs:
Accordions are wrappers for <je-link href="../je-details">JeDetails</je-link>. When an inner detail is opened, the others are automatically closed.
The implementation follows the [aria implementation of an accordion](https://www.w3.org/WAI/ARIA/apg/patterns/accordion/).

usage.closable:
Adding the `closable` attribute will display a close icon in the top right that hides the alert on click. ::: live-code-demo ```html home
Hello there
Where's the chapstick? ``` :::
usage.slots:
The `end` slot can be used for action items like buttons

::: live-code-demo

```html
<je-alert open>
  <je-icon slot="start">settings</je-icon>
  Where's the chapstick?
  <je-button fill="outline" size="sm" slot="end">Undo</je-button>
  <je-button fill="outline" size="sm" slot="end">Dismiss</je-button>
</je-alert>
```

:::
